tw電影配樂其實都麻麻..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  太熱血feel 感覺錯左feeling"},{"pid":"65723b53d118cdf1c9caae27d8217682134eaffe","tid":280091,"uid":100756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T00:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://tombofdolls.blogspot.hk/2017/06/blame.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftombofdolls.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F06%2Fblame.html&d=N8xYUS4A8HlYY7RRcLmgcIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=38a84cbf\" target=\"_blank\">http://tombofdolls.blogspot.hk/2017/06/blame.html</a><br />\n<br />\n之前寫左篇文 一d觀點同你差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過你介紹比較清晰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw電影配樂其實都麻麻..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  太熱血feel 感覺錯左feeling</blockquote><br />\n嘩, 你篇文好詳細, 好多內容都好淸楚, 大推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我怕片長太耐所以跳過好多內容, 想簡化得黎有重點<br />\n你覺得可以我就安心啦<br />\n<br />\n其實錄完稿先醒起漏左配樂...不過中規中矩, 所以唔提算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2236ac0ec175d58178d9e3b5a8467257bd051be7","tid":280091,"uid":68058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T01:04:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://tombofdolls.blogspot.hk/2017/06/blame.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftombofdolls.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F06%2Fblame.html&d=N8xYUS4A8HlYY7RRcLmgcIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=38a84cbf\" target=\"_blank\">http://tombofdolls.blogspot.hk/2017/06/blame.html</a><br />\n<br />\n之前寫左篇文 一d觀點同你差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過你介紹比較清晰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw電影配樂其實都麻麻..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  太熱血feel 感覺錯左feeling</blockquote><br />\n嘩, 你篇文好詳細, 好多內容都好淸楚, 大推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.g